###train and test split

set.seed(19)
n_data <- nrow(clean_thrones)
test_index <- sample(1:n_data, size = n_data * .2)

thrones_test <- slice(clean_thrones, test_index)
thrones_train <- slice(clean_thrones, -test_index)
thrones_test %>% 
  tabyl(dth_flag)
